    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1424600/extras/a21f303905c44dd2ea3a8007c4e7e712.avif?t=1772111310\" width=616 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1424600/extras/edb0161b9db9f6489684d466613502c3.webp?t=1772111310\" width=616 height=1 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1424600/extras/89a3bb73320d3fd00a55a6c3a1221fbf.poster.avif?t=1772111310\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1424600/extras/89a3bb73320d3fd00a55a6c3a1221fbf.webm?t=1772111310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1424600/extras/89a3bb73320d3fd00a55a6c3a1221fbf.mp4?t=1772111310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>惊悚离奇</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时值1888年，对抗残暴“国家”的战争已到生死关头，滨海之地赫墨拉危于累卵。为了拯救国家，儒勒·凡尔纳与尼摩船长决定孤注一掷，驾驶声名狼藉的“鹦鹉螺号”潜艇深潜搜寻传说中的亚特兰蒂斯。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据传说，那里埋藏着一件有着足以改变历史进程的古代秘宝：赫菲斯托斯之焰！正是它的力量让亚特兰蒂斯崛起与衰落。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在他们的冒险中，儒勒·凡尔纳不仅将发现超乎想象的奇观与秘密，更将遭遇一位强大的黑暗使徒，其唯一目的便是将赫墨拉中所有人的想象力抹杀 – 凡尔纳本人也不例外！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1424600/extras/87bf634c6e3bc8aa3590ee7b995bd1f8.poster.avif?t=1772111310\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1424600/extras/87bf634c6e3bc8aa3590ee7b995bd1f8.webm?t=1772111310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1424600/extras/87bf634c6e3bc8aa3590ee7b995bd1f8.mp4?t=1772111310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>发挥想象力:</strong> 利用亚特兰蒂斯秘宝IMAG的力量来重写历史，并在重要关头改写儒勒的命运。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独特故事:</strong> 一千个读者眼中就会有一千个哈姆雷特。本作的非线性对话会让每个玩家的游戏体验各有不同。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>深海寻宝:</strong> 游戏受经典冒险游戏启发，解开谜题，探索环境将是成功的关键。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>掘地三尺:</strong> 从鹦鹉螺号的幽暗过道，到亚特兰蒂斯的古代遗迹 - 充满细节和氛围感的蒸汽朋克像素美术等待您的挖掘。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>深入细节:</strong> 亲身参与，成为儒勒·凡尔纳作品与人生故事的一部分吧。</p></li></ul>",
